cat << EOF
Gurgitate-mail is a mail delivery agent. It has two things going for it:
 * It's small and easy to use.
 * It has configuration files in Ruby, which is approximately eight
   thousand times easier to read and write than Procmail's line noise,
   and yet much more powerful.
 Contributed by Dave Brown, dagbrown@lart.ca
EOF

